    "PR #186 review fixes are loaded before the main entrypoint so custom RunId discovery, invalid-window fallback, and validation-only padding gates are active in the compiled runtime output.",
    "PR #186 external review fixes are loaded before the main entrypoint so exact custom RunId collect roots are purged before reuse without broadening blank/latest cleanup.",
    "PR #212 metadata finalization fixes are loaded through connector-friendly 04H1, 04H2, and 04H3 parts before the main entrypoint so collect upload guidance can reference the final metadata report path without snapshotting a placeholder file.",
    "Part 01 core utilities are split into connector-friendly 01A1, 01A2, 01B1, 01B2, 01C, 01D1, 01D2, and 01E functional source parts while preserving the compiled single-runtime collector output.",
    "Collector part files must not define the same PowerShell function name more than once across wrapper and part load order; duplicate function definitions are a package-validation failure.",
    "Script entries in this artifact intentionally end in .txt to bypass mail filters.",
